Tambah dia teman di LINE, lalu ucapkan terima kasih.

138
00:08:26,986 --> 00:08:28,706
-Kenapa aku harus gitu? -Ayo dong.

139
00:08:29,161 --> 00:08:31,788
Kamu hutang sama dia, nggak ada pilihan.

140
00:08:32,585 --> 00:08:33,309
Ayo!

141
00:08:33,845 --> 00:08:35,284
Tambah aja, kasih HP-mu sini.

142
00:08:35,315 --> 00:08:38,140
-Ayo, tambah aja. -Ya, deh.

143
00:08:40,663 --> 00:08:41,711
Sudah aku add.

144
00:08:42,474 --> 00:08:43,710
