192
00:11:11,441 --> 00:11:13,918
Aku cuma nemenin, aku udah makan tadi.

193
00:11:14,195 --> 00:11:17,158
Baiklah, aku tanya Ket sama Q dulu.

194
00:11:17,762 --> 00:11:19,352
Toh aku juga mau ngobrol sama mereka.

195
00:11:20,102 --> 00:11:22,000
Kita ketemu di tempat P'Yah, ya.

196
00:11:22,927 --> 00:11:24,148
Yakin, nih?

197
