Jangan gitu, kalau mukaku luka lagi—

211
00:12:04,370 --> 00:12:05,856
Cewek-cewek bakal ilfeel sama aku.

212
00:12:07,899 --> 00:12:09,134
Oh iya.

213
00:12:09,358 --> 00:12:10,918
Maaf soal semalam.

214
00:12:11,971 --> 00:12:12,910
Santai aja.

215
00:12:13,044 --> 00:12:14,910
Aku sendiri yang mulai ribut sama mereka.

216
00:12:15,167 --> 00:12:16,910
Bukan kamu yang maksa aku.

217
00:12:17,715 --> 00:12:19,440
