Kalau dia bisa sampai ngerusak hp-ku kayak gitu,

245
00:13:39,208 --> 00:13:41,420
pasti dia memang kelihatan serem.

246
00:13:42,602 --> 00:13:43,536
Tunggu deh.

247
00:13:44,011 --> 00:13:44,961
Tadi...

248
00:13:45,201 --> 00:13:46,960
Siapa tadi yang ngerusak hp kamu?

249
00:13:47,832 --> 00:13:49,918
P'Johan.

250
00:13:50,949 --> 00:13:52,438
Dia yang ngerusak hp-ku.

251
00:13:52,604 --> 00:13:53,792
Nih, lihat.

252
00:13:53,842 --> 00:13:55,790
Kayak abis diinjek orang.

253
00:13:56,429 --> 00:13:57,790
Nggak bisa dinyalain, liat deh.

254
00:13:58,210 --> 00:13:59,790
Siapa yang bilang?

255
00:14:13,733 --> 00:14:14,949
Sialan.

256
00:14:15,388 --> 00:14:16,940
Kenapa nggak ngasih tahu aku?

257
00:14:17,066 --> 00:14:19,094
Aku sampe teriak-teriak ke dia gitu lagi.

258
00:14:19,724 --> 00:14:22,930
Mana aku tau kamu lupa semua.

259
00:14:23,340 --> 00:14:24,285
Gawat banget.

260
00:14:31,826 --> 00:14:33,955
Oh, kamu datang.

261
00:14:36,025 --> 00:14:37,380
Ada apa?

262
00:14:38,001 --> 00:14:39,854
Hei, North.

263
00:14:43,460 --> 00:14:45,222
Mukamu kenapa?

264
00:14:46,241 --> 00:14:48,017
Barusan kena masalah.

265
00:14:48,266 --> 00:14:49,217
Aduh, astaga.

266
00:14:49,311 --> 00:14:51,588
Muka sekeren ini sekarang lebam semua.

267
00:14:51,634 --> 00:14:53,405
Hampir nggak kenal kamu, North.

268
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,700
Sakit nggak? Sini aku liat.

269
00:14:56,300 --> 00:14:58,637
Biasanya sih nggak sakit, tapi ditekan—

270
00:14:58,820 --> 00:15:00,630
-jadinya sakit. -Maaf ya.

271
00:15:01,173 --> 00:15:04,877
Kamu kenapa sih? Masih bisa kerja nggak?

272
00:15:04,948 --> 00:15:06,930
Bisa kok, aku nggak apa-apa.

273
00:15:07,041 --> 00:15:08,930
Jangan sampai kejadian gini lagi, ya?

274
00:15:09,013 --> 00:15:10,930
Ayo ganti baju dulu.

275
00:15:10,930 --> 00:15:12,127
Oke.

276
00:15:13,527 --> 00:15:14,850
Ayo gih.

277
00:15:22,902 --> 00:15:24,736
(North, kamu oke? Temp udah cerita semua.)

278
00:15:24,762 --> 00:15:26,730
(Sebenarnya ada apa? Bisa cerita nggak?)

279
00:15:26,770 --> 00:15:29,604
(Katanya yang nolong kamu itu kakak kelas mereka, jadi dia nggak mau bikin ribut.)

280
00:15:29,860 --> 00:15:32,400
(Tungguin balasanmu nih, aku khawatir. Kita masih teman kan.)

281
00:15:33,165 --> 00:15:35,047
(Apa sih yang terjadi semalam?)

282
00:15:35,047 --> 00:15:37,040
(Temp bilang kamu tiba-tiba nerobos, tapi aku tahu kamu bukan begitu.)

283
00:15:37,040 --> 00:15:38,223
(Apa Temp selingkuh ya?)

284
00:15:38,331 --> 00:15:39,268
(Kamu tahu nggak?)

285
00:15:42,602 --> 00:15:43,721
(Mungkin nggak kok.)

286
00:15:47,340 --> 00:15:50,988
(Aku baru jadian sama Temp, kalau dia punya orang lain, aku nggak bisa lanjut sama dia.)

287
00:15:54,500 --> 00:15:56,592
(Mungkin itu cuma salah paham.)

288
00:15:57,620 --> 00:15:59,122
(Semoga memang begitu.)

289
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:02,336
(North, aku boleh chat kamu lagi nggak? Sebagai teman.)

290
00:16:02,348 --> 00:16:04,330
(Cuma waktu ngobrol sama kamu aku bisa jadi diri sendiri.)

291
00:16:07,154 --> 00:16:09,220
Tentu. Kalau aku sempat, pasti aku balas.

292
00:16:12,830 --> 00:16:13,967
-North. -Hei.

293
00:16:13,970 --> 00:16:15,318
Ngapain kamu?

294
00:16:15,976 --> 00:16:17,960
Katanya kamu nggak bakal hubungi dia lagi?

295
00:16:18,782 --> 00:16:22,280
Dia chat aku, katanya abis ribut sama pacarnya.

296
00:16:22,358 --> 00:16:23,540
Yakin?

297
00:16:23,594 --> 00:16:26,170
Jangan sampe aku tahu kalau kamu suka dia lagi.

298
00:16:26,183 --> 00:16:28,860
Kalau kamu minum gara-gara dia lagi, awas aja.

299
00:16:29,751 --> 00:16:31,939
Udah, gitu aja.

300
00:16:32,386 --> 00:16:34,040
Tapi aku masih nggak ngerti.

301
00:16:34,040 --> 00:16:38,017
Dia santai banget, padahal dulu dia yang ninggalin aku.

302
00:16:38,447 --> 00:16:40,414
Soalnya dia anggap kamu teman.

303
00:16:40,548 --> 00:16:42,808
Dia bisa jadi diri sendiri waktu ngobrol sama kamu.

304
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:44,294
Kenapa sih, cerita kaya gitu lagi?

305
00:16:44,330 --> 00:16:47,216
Janji nggak bakal balik ke dia lagi?

306
00:16:47,478 --> 00:16:49,635
Aku nggak mau lihat kamu kayak semalam lagi.

307
00:16:51,955 --> 00:16:54,035
Tenang, aku nggak bakal balikan kok.

308
00:16:54,312 --> 00:16:55,717
Hmm.

309
00:17:00,995 --> 00:17:03,432
Aku tunggu di luar.

310
00:17:05,989 --> 00:17:08,666
Oke, sayang.

311
00:17:08,680 --> 00:17:11,988
Jangan gitu, aku kangen kamu.

312
00:17:12,780 --> 00:17:14,594
Daging sapinya datang nih.

313
00:17:17,099 --> 00:17:18,586
-North, North... -Apa?

314
00:17:20,451 --> 00:17:22,768
Tolong antarin pesanan ini, bisa?

315
00:17:22,859 --> 00:17:25,219
-Oke, P'Yah. -Makasih.

316
00:17:25,314 --> 00:17:27,797
Siap, sampai nanti.

317
00:17:31,060 --> 00:17:32,186
Oh.

318
00:17:32,708 --> 00:17:34,180
Kenapa kamu ke sini, Johan?

319
00:17:36,266 --> 00:17:37,320
Oh.

320
00:17:39,911 --> 00:17:40,888
Eh...

321
00:17:41,096 --> 00:17:44,002
Soal handphone.

322
00:17:44,223 --> 00:17:45,632
Maaf, ya.

323
00:17:45,802 --> 00:17:48,496
-Aku nggak tau — bunga gimana?

324
00:17:48,958 --> 00:17:51,150
Bisa nggak bunganya diturunin?

325
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:53,520
Aku bakal cicil perlahan hutangnya.

326
00:17:58,056 --> 00:18:00,072
Aku bisa hapus bunganya.

327
00:18:00,976 --> 00:18:03,682
Tapi kamu harus nurut semua syaratku.

328
00:18:04,472 --> 00:18:06,871
Serius nggak ada bunga?

329
00:18:06,910 --> 00:18:09,042
Mau nggak jalani syaratku?

330
00:18:09,274 --> 00:18:11,306
Kamu mau aku ngapain?

331
00:18:17,302 --> 00:18:18,503
Hoi!

332
00:18:19,420 --> 00:18:20,666
Kapan-kapan aja deh bahasnya.

333
00:18:20,881 --> 00:18:23,171
Tunggu, P'Johan! Bungaku gimana?

334
00:18:26,247 --> 00:18:27,437
Makasih udah berlangganan.

335
00:18:30,757 --> 00:18:32,197
Kenapa lama banget di luar?

336
00:18:32,700 --> 00:18:34,746
Tadi sama P'Johan.

337
00:18:34,760 --> 00:18:37,134
P'Johan? Dia ngapain?

338
00:18:37,331 --> 00:18:39,192
Dia bilang nggak akan ambil bunga lagi.

339
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:40,576
Serius?

340
00:18:40,657 --> 00:18:42,740
Emang bagus sih, pasti ngebantu aku banget.

341
00:18:42,807 --> 00:18:45,297
Tapi dia bilang...

342
00:18:45,410 --> 00:18:47,952
Aku harus nurut syarat dia.

343
00:18:48,460 --> 00:18:50,118
-Apa aja? -Iya.

344
00:18:50,235 --> 00:18:52,605
Apa sih syaratnya itu?

345
00:18:52,834 --> 00:18:54,053
Iya juga...

346
00:18:54,434 --> 00:18:55,949
Aku juga nggak tahu.

347
00:18:56,383 --> 00:18:58,349
Tiba-tiba dia telponan terus pergi.

348
00:18:59,124 --> 00:19:01,131
Gimana kalau aku dijadiin asistennya?

349
00:19:01,254 --> 00:19:02,579
Nggak seburuk itu, sih.

350
00:19:02,600 --> 00:19:04,800
Katanya kamu harus siap lakuin apa saja.

351
00:19:04,891 --> 00:19:07,200
Kalau dia nyuruh kamu hal haram gimana?

352
00:19:07,200 --> 00:19:09,874
Bisa-bisa kamu tambah masalah.

353
00:19:09,912 --> 00:19:11,870
Nggak bakal gitu, kok.

354
00:19:14,080 --> 00:19:15,401
Tetep aja bisa.

355
00:19:15,438 --> 00:19:18,850
Mungkin aja separah itu.

356
00:19:18,865 --> 00:19:19,610
Nggak akan.

357
00:19:19,617 --> 00:19:21,120
Bisa jadi.

358
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:23,120
Kayaknya mungkin aja.

359
00:19:27,745 --> 00:19:29,687
Kalian nggak ada kerjaan?

360
00:19:29,807 --> 00:19:31,154
Ada, kok.

361
00:19:32,102 --> 00:19:36,385
-Ada tamu, layani dulu. Halo! -Silakan masuk!

362
00:19:37,032 --> 00:19:38,866
Silakan masuk.

363
00:19:40,087 --> 00:19:41,198
Ayo, masuk.

364
00:19:46,515 --> 00:19:48,151
P'Yah, nggak kerja nih?

365
00:19:48,880 --> 00:19:51,020
Ngapain berdiri di sini?

366
00:19:51,057 --> 00:19:53,020
Anak ini, buruan sana!

367
00:20:00,890 --> 00:20:02,868
Kami pulang, P'Yah.

368
00:20:02,887 --> 00:20:05,565
-Da... -Oke, makasih hari ini!

369
00:20:05,632 --> 00:20:07,647
Kalian pulang naik apa?

370
00:20:07,727 --> 00:20:11,558
Hill bakal jemput kalian kayak biasa?

371
00:20:12,308 --> 00:20:13,256
Iya.

372
00:20:15,373 --> 00:20:17,051
Aku sampe iri sama kamu, Ter.

373
00:20:17,128 --> 00:20:19,690
Aku juga pengen dijemput gitu.

374
00:20:20,191 --> 00:20:21,788
Jujur, aku malah jadi sebel.

375
00:20:21,860 --> 00:20:24,358
Kalo bareng bertiga, aku jadi pengganggu aja.

376
00:20:24,422 --> 00:20:27,557
Tapi nggak papa, aku juga senang kalau mereka bareng.

377
00:20:27,610 --> 00:20:29,980
-Bisa tahan deh! -Alah, sotoy.

378
00:20:30,080 --> 00:20:32,991
-Kami pergi, da P'Yah! -Suka saling godain emang!

379
00:20:33,050 --> 00:20:34,860
-Sana jalan. -Malu-malu dulu, ya.

380
00:20:34,875 --> 00:20:36,860
-North— -Huh, rasanya jatuh cinta.

381
00:20:37,121 --> 00:20:38,237
Aku paham, kok.

382
00:20:38,682 --> 00:20:39,856
Aku tahu kamu bercanda.

383
00:20:39,950 --> 00:20:41,945
Aku tadi denger kamu teleponan sama orang lain.

384
00:20:43,608 --> 00:20:44,644
Sama siapa?

385
00:20:44,690 --> 00:20:47,192
Aku lagi nelpon cewek, Krub.

386
00:20:47,810 --> 00:20:49,189
Pake "Krub" segala.

387
00:20:49,703 --> 00:20:50,801
-Da. -Dadah.

388
00:21:00,850 --> 00:21:02,294
Capek banget, ya?

389
00:21:02,601 --> 00:21:03,851
Nggak capek sama sekali kok.

390
00:21:03,988 --> 00:21:06,340
-Halo, North. -Halo, P'Hill.

391
00:21:06,856 --> 00:21:08,315
Mau makan malam nggak?

392
00:21:08,346 --> 00:21:09,933
Mau.

393
00:21:25,820 --> 00:21:27,183
Mau nambah apa lagi, North?

394
00:21:27,576 --> 00:21:28,890
Nggak, udah cukup.

395
00:21:29,905 --> 00:21:31,019
Nih buat kamu.

396
00:21:37,360 --> 00:21:38,960
Oh P'Hill

397
00:21:39,020 --> 00:21:41,380
Hari ini P'Johan ke tempat kerja North.

398
00:21:41,933 --> 00:21:43,545
Johan, ya?

399
00:21:44,240 --> 00:21:47,278
Katanya dia tidak akan menarik bunga dari North lagi.

400
00:21:47,934 --> 00:21:52,880
Tapi North harus menuruti semua permintaannya.

401
00:21:53,631 --> 00:21:54,940
Dia benar-benar bilang begitu?

402
00:21:55,524 --> 00:21:56,637
Ya.

403
00:21:56,896 --> 00:21:58,552
Apa yang dia mau aku lakukan?

404
00:21:59,536 --> 00:22:00,968
Aku juga tidak tahu.

405
00:22:01,389 --> 00:22:04,389
Kamu sudah tanya dia, dia mau apa?

406
00:22:04,605 --> 00:22:06,832
Sudah kutanya.

407
00:22:07,102 --> 00:22:08,965
Tapi ada yang menelpon dia.

408
00:22:09,586 --> 00:22:12,404
Dia pergi setelah angkat telepon.

409
00:22:13,608 --> 00:22:14,805
Akhir-akhir ini dia agak sibuk.

410
00:22:15,127 --> 00:22:17,773
Coba kirim pesan saja, aku sudah kasih akun LINE-nya ke kamu.

411
00:22:20,465 --> 00:22:21,640
Akan kulakukan.

412
00:22:26,442 --> 00:22:28,240
Makasih.

413
00:22:29,084 --> 00:22:30,191
Ayo, kita pergi.

414
00:22:30,345 --> 00:22:31,548
-Ya. -Oke.

415
00:22:32,280 --> 00:22:34,928
-Kamu sudah kenyang? -Sudah.

416
00:22:37,395 --> 00:22:39,280
Bro, kenyang tanpa bayar, nih.

417
00:22:46,657 --> 00:22:49,386
Bro, dia kerja apa sih?

418
00:22:54,834 --> 00:22:55,724
Hmm.

419
00:22:55,872 --> 00:22:58,522
Kenapa? Aku cuma tanya.

420
00:22:58,823 --> 00:23:00,022
Oh.

421
00:23:00,102 --> 00:23:02,853
Mungkin bisnis keluarganya.

422
00:23:03,007 --> 00:23:04,654
Kerja untuk perusahaan keluarga?

423
00:23:04,721 --> 00:23:07,502
Jangan bilang kamu percaya deh.

424
00:23:09,174 --> 00:23:10,751
Lihat saja dia.

425
00:23:11,583 --> 00:23:14,694
Kalau dibilang dia nongkrong tiap hari, aku sih percaya.

426
00:23:17,364 --> 00:23:18,739
Aku harus gimana nih?

427
00:23:19,256 --> 00:23:20,687
Gimana apa?

428
00:23:20,696 --> 00:23:23,617
Kirim pesan, tanya dia mau apa.

429
00:23:23,645 --> 00:23:24,832
Ya, gitu saja.

430
00:23:24,885 --> 00:23:27,914
Kamu punya utang, nggak mau bayar bunga kan.

431
00:23:28,010 --> 00:23:29,565
Lakukan saja.

432
00:23:29,817 --> 00:23:31,380
Bener juga.

433
00:23:31,709 --> 00:23:34,037
Tapi kalau dia minta hal buruk kaya yang kamu bilang gimana?

434
00:23:34,402 --> 00:23:36,906
Kalau nggak tanya, kamu nggak bakal tahu.

435
00:23:37,352 --> 00:23:38,994
Ter, aku harus bagaimana?

436
00:23:54,720 --> 00:23:57,379
(Kamu bilang "sesuai kata kamu", maksudnya apa?)

437
00:23:57,391 --> 00:24:00,198
(Kalau nggak berlebihan, aku bisa kok. Atau mungkin bisa kurangin bunganya.)

438
00:24:03,217 --> 00:24:04,642
Dia sudah baca.

439
00:24:09,696 --> 00:24:10,400
Bro.

440
00:24:11,311 --> 00:24:13,262
Dia cuma baca, nggak balas.

441
00:24:13,451 --> 00:24:14,740
Haruskah aku kirim lagi?

442
00:24:14,835 --> 00:24:16,957
Tentu, kirim saja.

443
00:24:16,997 --> 00:24:18,845
Kalau kamu nggak takut dia marah.

444
00:24:19,414 --> 00:24:21,185
Jangan ngomong gitu dong.

445
00:24:21,604 --> 00:24:23,294
Aku cuma mau tahu.

446
00:24:23,405 --> 00:24:26,180
Gimana kalau dia berubah pikiran?

447
00:24:26,441 --> 00:24:27,945
Ini sepuluh ribu baht, bro.

448
00:24:28,040 --> 00:24:30,016
Terserah kamu.

449
00:24:46,853 --> 00:24:48,900
(Sekarang kamu kerja?)

450
00:24:48,910 --> 00:24:51,608
(Aku nggak mau ganggu, tapi ada waktu nggak?)

451
00:25:02,390 --> 00:25:04,342
(Aku cuma mau pastiin, kamu nggak ambil bunga?)

452
00:25:04,354 --> 00:25:05,770
(Beneran?)

453
00:25:12,078 --> 00:25:14,278
Dia sudah baca, tapi nggak balas.

454
00:25:15,537 --> 00:25:19,115
Mungkin dia lagi marah.

455
00:25:20,675 --> 00:25:21,462
Hei.

456
00:25:21,743 --> 00:25:23,848
Dia sedang balas.

457
00:25:24,228 --> 00:25:25,840
Jawabannya lima detik lagi.

458
00:25:26,680 --> 00:25:27,720
(Johan)

459
00:25:31,872 --> 00:25:33,565
Halo.

460
00:25:37,967 --> 00:25:39,554
Kamu lagi kerja?

461
00:25:40,813 --> 00:25:43,211
Iya, malas kirim pesan. Kenapa?

462
00:25:45,023 --> 00:25:47,995
Mau nanya soal bunga, boleh?

463
00:25:49,432 --> 00:25:51,100
Jadi boleh atau nggak?

464
00:25:51,619 --> 00:25:52,579
Ini...

465
00:25:53,238 --> 00:25:56,398
Kamu bilang "semua permintaanmu".

466
00:25:56,442 --> 00:25:58,390
Aku harus ngapain?

467
00:25:58,958 --> 00:26:01,591
Kalau nggak aneh-aneh, aku bisa kok.

468
00:26:04,048 --> 00:26:06,122
Permintaan kayak apa yang keterlaluan?

469
00:26:07,460 --> 00:26:11,204
Contohnya, suruh aku melanggar hukum.

470
00:26:11,300 --> 00:26:12,574
Kayak jual narkoba.

471
00:26:12,656 --> 00:26:13,998
Atau mencuri dompet orang.

472
00:26:14,034 --> 00:26:15,905
Merampok toko emas.

473
00:26:16,545 --> 00:26:18,647
Atau menyakiti orang lain.

474
00:26:18,755 --> 00:26:20,936
Hal itu tidak bisa aku lakukan, bro.

475
00:26:20,967 --> 00:26:25,536
Kamu nggak suruh aku aneh-aneh kan?

476
00:26:26,106 --> 00:26:29,198
Menurutmu kamu sanggup melakukan itu?

477
00:26:29,214 --> 00:26:31,190
Nggak.

478
00:26:32,108 --> 00:26:34,300
Tenang, nggak akan di luar kemampuanmu.

479
00:26:34,420 --> 00:26:35,348
Oke.

480
00:26:35,385 --> 00:26:37,672
Kemampuanku juga nggak banyak.

481
00:26:37,808 --> 00:26:38,682
Baguslah.

482
00:26:39,300 --> 00:26:42,127
Kalau gitu, nggak usah deh, kamu payah.

483
00:26:43,906 --> 00:26:45,690
Eh, gitu ya...

484
00:26:46,253 --> 00:26:48,517
Aku akan lakukan semua yang kamu mau.

485
00:26:49,037 --> 00:26:51,232
Tapi jangan tarik bunga dariku.

486
00:26:52,094 --> 00:26:53,288
Hmm.

487
00:26:53,653 --> 00:26:54,834
Tapi...

488
00:26:54,917 --> 00:26:56,638
Kalau kamu bikin aku kesal,

489
00:26:56,832 --> 00:26:58,357
aku bakal hitung bunga harian.

490
00:26:58,445 --> 00:27:00,377
Hey, kok gitu sih?

491
00:27:01,002 --> 00:27:03,062
Nggak boleh?

492
00:27:04,109 --> 00:27:05,496
Boleh.

493
00:27:08,512 --> 00:27:09,601
Lagi...

494
00:27:09,677 --> 00:27:11,315
Apa yang bikin kamu marah?

495
00:27:11,545 --> 00:27:12,798
Pikir sendiri.

496
00:27:13,125 --> 00:27:15,429
Hei, mana aku tahu.

497
00:27:17,484 --> 00:27:18,720
Diamlah.

498
00:27:18,914 --> 00:27:20,100
Jangan sampai ketiduran.

499
00:27:20,354 --> 00:27:21,838
Jangan bikin suara apapun.

500
00:27:23,481 --> 00:27:26,174
Maksudmu cuma mau di sini aja?

501
00:27:38,737 --> 00:27:40,048
Mau aku temani ngobrol?

502
00:27:45,097 --> 00:27:48,142
Hei, kamu yang suruh aku ke sini, aku harus ngomong dong.

503
00:27:48,702 --> 00:27:52,367
Dulu mantanku, Jah, kalau mau tutup telepon, suruh aku terus ngomong.

504
00:27:55,429 --> 00:27:57,182
Aku bukan mantanmu.

505
00:28:01,275 --> 00:28:02,416
Oke deh.

506
00:28:03,321 --> 00:28:04,893
Aku bakal diem.

507
00:28:13,379 --> 00:28:14,727
P'Johan

508
00:28:14,773 --> 00:28:16,317
Aku ngantuk.

509
00:28:16,358 --> 00:28:17,958
Masih lama lagi?

510
00:28:18,604 --> 00:28:19,917
Sebentar lagi.

511
00:28:24,825 --> 00:28:27,211
Kamu selalu kerja sampai larut tiap hari?

512
00:28:27,331 --> 00:28:28,949
Nggak juga, cuma kadang-kadang.

513
00:28:32,339 --> 00:28:34,111
Kamu bisa ngobrol sama aku nggak?

514
00:28:36,862 --> 00:28:38,133
Aku cuma mau kamu di sini.

515
00:28:38,390 --> 00:28:39,777
Masih harus temani ngobrol juga?

516
00:28:39,808 --> 00:28:42,373
Iya, aku cuma ngantuk.

517
00:28:42,767 --> 00:28:44,090
Ceritain dong tentang kamu.

518
00:28:44,090 --> 00:28:47,502
Ceritaku?

519
00:28:48,463 --> 00:28:51,623
Ceritaku banyak, mau dengar yang mana?

520
00:28:55,945 --> 00:28:57,134
Halo, aku North.

521
00:28:57,546 --> 00:29:01,242
North, nama lengkap Natchanan, mahasiswa teknik tahun satu.

522
00:29:01,417 --> 00:29:02,582
Wah.

523
00:29:02,862 --> 00:29:05,290
Baru pembuka aja udah keren, kan?

524
00:29:05,355 --> 00:29:07,087
Teman sekamarku namanya Anak Paskah.

525
00:29:07,217 --> 00:29:09,737
Aku santai, agak dingin.

526
00:29:09,752 --> 00:29:11,730
Nggak terlalu serius dalam hidup.

527
00:29:12,564 --> 00:29:13,828
Aku santai dan bahagia.

528
00:29:13,922 --> 00:29:16,699
Lucu dan mudah dirawat.

529
00:29:16,817 --> 00:29:18,360
Selalu rendah hati ke orang tua.

530
00:29:18,560 --> 00:29:22,237
Aku teman semua orang, hormati siapapun.

531
00:29:22,783 --> 00:29:24,737
Boleh nggak sih muji diri sendiri gitu?

532
00:29:25,125 --> 00:29:28,771
Bukan kata aku, itu di raport buat orang tuaku.

533
00:29:29,490 --> 00:29:30,401
Tapi...

534
00:29:30,437 --> 00:29:34,240
Bagian "lucu dan mudah dirawat" itu tambahanku sendiri.

535
00:29:43,189 --> 00:29:45,671
Kamu juga mau kenalin diri nggak?

536
00:29:45,973 --> 00:29:49,274
-Kenapa pilih fakultas kedokteran? -Jangan ngomong.

537
00:29:53,241 --> 00:29:54,840
Tapi aku ngantuk.

538
00:29:55,084 --> 00:29:57,594
Aku nggak suka kopi kayak kamu.

539
00:29:58,211 --> 00:29:59,500
Kok kamu tahu?

540
00:29:59,720 --> 00:30:01,032
Cuma tebak aja.

541
00:30:01,084 --> 00:30:04,745
Kamu sering kerja malam, pasti kecanduan kopi.

542
00:30:05,520 --> 00:30:06,740
Hei.

543
00:30:06,914 --> 00:30:08,743
Aku mau belajar bikin kopi.

544
00:30:09,080 --> 00:30:12,512
Nanti kalau sudah bisa, kamu coba, ya.

545
00:30:14,185 --> 00:30:15,481
Belajar buat kopi.

546
00:30:15,681 --> 00:30:16,638
Iya.

547
00:30:16,717 --> 00:30:20,368
Tahu nggak, aku kerja di kafe kopi.

548
00:30:20,691 --> 00:30:21,722
Kafe yang mana?

549
00:30:22,226 --> 00:30:23,890
Dekat kampus.

550
00:30:23,986 --> 00:30:25,291
Aku dan Anak Paskah juga kerja di sana.

551
00:30:25,687 --> 00:30:26,795
Mau dapat duit lebih banyak?

552
00:30:26,835 --> 00:30:27,816
Tentu saja.

553
00:30:27,844 --> 00:30:29,918
Masih banyak utang yang harus dibayar.

554
00:30:30,056 --> 00:30:34,527
Jujur, aku mau kerja lebih banyak lagi.

555
00:30:35,001 --> 00:30:37,460
Tapi aku nggak bakal tarik bunga lagi darimu.

556
00:30:37,773 --> 00:30:39,875
Hey, siapa tahu nanti berubah pikiran.

557
00:30:40,478 --> 00:30:42,309
Gimana kalau kamu tiba-tiba narik bunga lagi?

558
00:30:42,955 --> 00:30:44,300
Kamu itu misterius banget.

559
00:30:55,160 --> 00:30:56,974
Boleh tanya sesuatu nggak?

560
00:30:58,641 --> 00:31:01,442
Orang yang bersamamu suka ngeluh nggak sih?

561
00:31:03,192 --> 00:31:04,164
Nggak.

562
00:31:06,256 --> 00:31:07,442
Serius?

563
00:31:09,868 --> 00:31:11,657
Aku nggak pernah biarin siapapun deket aku.

564
00:31:12,607 --> 00:31:14,152
Jangan terlalu banyak nanya, ya?

565
00:31:16,223 --> 00:31:17,617
Baiklah.

566
00:31:35,155 --> 00:31:36,117
North

567
00:31:39,182 --> 00:31:40,266
North

568
00:31:40,977 --> 00:31:42,268
North

569
00:31:43,232 --> 00:31:44,419
North

570
00:32:13,911 --> 00:32:15,551
(Kalau lelah, tiduran aja ya.)

571
00:32:21,324 --> 00:32:23,663
(Jangan kerja sampingan lagi, paham?)

572
00:32:49,108 --> 00:32:50,108
(Johan: Kalau ngantuk, tidur aja ya.)

573
00:32:56,108 --> 00:32:57,337
North

574
00:32:58,708 --> 00:32:59,946
Aku dukung kamu.

575
00:33:05,314 --> 00:33:06,680
Soal P'Jo itu.

576
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:08,080
Aku lihat chat kalian, lucu banget.

577
00:33:08,080 --> 00:33:09,321
Kalian berdua, aku suka banget!

578
00:33:09,731 --> 00:33:11,137
Suka apanya, aduh, lebay!

579
00:33:13,394 --> 00:33:15,069
Sebentar deh.

580
00:33:16,125 --> 00:33:17,902
Kok kamu tahu sih?

581
00:33:17,980 --> 00:33:19,900
Aduh.

582
00:33:20,912 --> 00:33:23,543
-Kamu nguping ya? -Nggak kok.

583
00:33:23,554 --> 00:33:24,764
Aku dengar nggak sengaja.

584
00:33:24,797 --> 00:33:26,580
Tapi aku nggak jelas dengarnya.

585
00:33:26,637 --> 00:33:29,309
Cuma kedengaran suara imut.

586
00:33:29,362 --> 00:33:31,300
-Imut banget! -Imut apanya?!

587
00:33:31,899 --> 00:33:33,300
Udah, jangan ganggu.

588
00:33:33,358 --> 00:33:36,481
Sayang sekali, aku udah jadi penggemar CP Johan dan North.

589
00:33:37,315 --> 00:33:39,632
Udah, jangan ngaco. Cepet masuk kelas!

590
00:33:41,510 --> 00:33:42,804
Aku pergi dulu.

591
00:33:42,931 --> 00:33:43,680
Oke.

592
00:33:43,736 --> 00:33:45,160
Temanku nggak kesepian lagi sekarang.

593
00:33:45,400 --> 00:33:47,823
Sekarang dia ada tempat buat curhat kapan saja.

594
00:33:48,460 --> 00:33:50,395
-Daah. -Ya.

595
00:33:55,696 --> 00:33:56,943
Apaan sih?

596
00:34:06,074 --> 00:34:08,460
-Apakah semuanya lancar hari ini? -Iya, Pak Ketua.

597
00:34:08,582 --> 00:34:10,460
Sisanya aku serahkan padamu.

598
00:34:24,300 --> 00:34:25,177
P'Hill

599
00:34:25,225 --> 00:34:26,880
Hari ini senior akan kumpul
dengan mahasiswa baru.

600
00:34:26,880 --> 00:34:28,270
Boleh aku ikut juga?

601
00:34:28,271 --> 00:34:29,442
Tentu saja bisa.

602
00:34:29,546 --> 00:34:31,600
Kamu sudah ambil banyak foto hari ini.

603
00:34:31,672 --> 00:34:32,602
Terima kasih.

604
00:34:32,714 --> 00:34:34,060
Kamu ada kelas hari ini?

605
00:34:34,066 --> 00:34:35,921
Ada, siang ini aku ada kelas.

606
00:34:36,522 --> 00:34:39,154
-Aku antar kamu. -Tidak usah, P'Hill.

607
00:34:39,223 --> 00:34:41,518
Kamu tetap di sini saja,
aku bisa pergi sendiri.

608
00:35:01,305 --> 00:35:02,591
Lucu sekali.

609
00:35:05,868 --> 00:35:07,179
Kamu suka?

610
00:35:08,394 --> 00:35:09,813
Suka.

611
00:35:11,850 --> 00:35:13,309
Aku juga suka.

612
00:36:00,954 --> 00:36:02,200
Semua sudah lengkap, kan?

613
00:36:02,211 --> 00:36:04,240
Kalian punya waktu satu minggu penuh

614
00:36:04,680 --> 00:36:08,780
untuk menemukan senior dengan nomor sama.

615
00:36:08,968 --> 00:36:12,647
Kami akan beri petunjuk tentang senior itu.

616
00:36:20,262 --> 00:36:25,637
Sampai jumpa di acara besok.

617
00:36:37,262 --> 00:36:39,400
Kalau menurutmu begitu,

618
00:36:39,828 --> 00:36:42,284
berarti kamu harus bayar utang padanya.

619
00:36:42,382 --> 00:36:45,305
Ya, makanya aku cari kerja sambilan lagi.

620
00:36:45,478 --> 00:36:46,491
Bro.

621
00:36:46,817 --> 00:36:49,777
Kalau butuh bantuan bilang saja,
aku juga merasa bersalah.

622
00:36:49,819 --> 00:36:52,367
Kenapa pas berantem kamu nggak mikir itu?

623
00:36:52,414 --> 00:36:53,977
Waktu itu kamu yang paling emosi!

624
00:36:53,977 --> 00:36:56,518
Mereka pukuli temanku,
masa aku cuma diam saja?

625
00:36:56,518 --> 00:36:58,110
-Jadi kamu terpaksa melawan? -Iya.

626
00:36:58,114 --> 00:37:00,634
Sudah! Jangan ribut.

627
00:37:01,515 --> 00:37:03,828
Utangku bukan gara-gara bar.

628
00:37:03,922 --> 00:37:05,499
Itu semua salahku sendiri.

629
00:37:06,189 --> 00:37:07,582
Memang kesalahanku.

630
00:37:07,638 --> 00:37:08,819
Pokoknya,

631
00:37:08,927 --> 00:37:11,085
kalau butuh bantuan, bilang ke kami.

632
00:37:17,939 --> 00:37:19,773
Halo North, aku Prang, asisten Johan.

633
00:37:19,783 --> 00:37:21,770
Aku yang urus keuangan dia.

634
00:37:21,786 --> 00:37:23,770
Kalau perlu kontak Johan, bilang ke aku.

635
00:37:23,785 --> 00:37:25,770
Kalau Johan potong jumlahnya,
aku juga akan kabari kamu.

636
00:37:28,077 --> 00:37:29,420
Tunggu.

637
00:37:29,442 --> 00:37:32,069
Katanya kamu kerja sambilan buat bayar utang.

638
00:37:32,216 --> 00:37:34,060
Tapi kok bisa beli ponsel baru?

639
00:37:36,197 --> 00:37:38,508
-Itu dari P'Johan. -Sialan.

640
00:37:38,564 --> 00:37:40,200
Kamu salahkan dia rusakkan ponselmu,

641
00:37:40,200 --> 00:37:41,844
tapi tetap dibelikan yang baru?

642
00:37:42,088 --> 00:37:43,225
Jadi?

643
00:37:43,789 --> 00:37:45,792
Ini agak mencurigakan, deh.

644
00:37:46,263 --> 00:37:48,312
Malam itu P'Johan yang jemput kamu.

645
00:37:48,549 --> 00:37:50,922
Terus, dia beliin kamu ponsel.

646
00:37:50,994 --> 00:37:53,943
Aku juga heran kenapa dia mau jemput kamu.

647
00:37:54,121 --> 00:37:56,654
Nggak ada apa-apa.

648
00:37:56,878 --> 00:37:58,668
Nggak terjadi apa pun.

649
00:37:58,709 --> 00:38:00,637
Jangan berpikiran aneh-aneh.

650
00:38:01,204 --> 00:38:05,585
Kata Ter, dia penggemar CP kalian.

651
00:38:05,786 --> 00:38:07,908
Boleh nggak aku ikutan baper juga? Aku jago, loh!

652
00:38:08,112 --> 00:38:11,805
Pulang aja sana baper sendiri,
semua CP-mu akan kuceraikan!

653
00:38:11,835 --> 00:38:14,457
Kok kalian tiba-tiba kompak gitu?

654
00:38:15,440 --> 00:38:18,228
Belum mulai baper, kalian sudah menyangkal duluan.

655
00:38:18,477 --> 00:38:20,293
Kenapa? Malu, ya?

656
00:38:23,290 --> 00:38:25,982
-Kamu merah, deh! -Aku mau ke kelas, waktunya sudah tiba!

657
00:38:26,029 --> 00:38:28,480
Kenapa tiba-tiba rajin kuliah?

658
00:38:28,480 --> 00:38:30,238
Aku memang selalu rajin kok.

659
00:38:31,229 --> 00:38:34,254
Kamu tahu nggak pelajaran apa hari ini?

660
00:38:34,277 --> 00:38:35,748
Ngaco, deh, kamu.

661
00:38:48,394 --> 00:38:50,031
Tuh, lihat saja.

662
00:38:50,548 --> 00:38:51,968
Para cewek pasti klepek-klepek sama dia.

663
00:38:52,623 --> 00:38:53,882
Ganteng banget.

664
00:38:54,103 --> 00:38:57,586
Kancingnya lupa, rambut acak-acakan,
tetap saja keren.

665
00:38:58,911 --> 00:39:00,680
Kamu naksir juga, ya?

666
00:39:01,502 --> 00:39:03,360
Kalau kamu lihat dia di depanku,

667
00:39:03,360 --> 00:39:05,240
pasti nggak anggap dia keren lagi!

668
00:39:05,758 --> 00:39:07,240
Sombong banget, sih.

669
00:39:13,048 --> 00:39:15,125
Kamu nggak tertarik?

670
00:39:15,207 --> 00:39:19,034
Dia ganteng dan kaya.

671
00:39:20,580 --> 00:39:22,740
Tapi gara-gara dia aku punya banyak utang!

672
00:39:23,460 --> 00:39:25,820
Menurutku, kalau kamu jadi pacarnya,

673
00:39:25,850 --> 00:39:29,620
utangmu pasti langsung lunas deh.

674
00:39:31,050 --> 00:39:33,510
Ngawur! Fokus ke pelajaran.

675
00:39:33,610 --> 00:39:34,600
Hei.

676
00:39:42,170 --> 00:39:43,440
Oke, aku tulis sekarang.

677
00:39:55,920 --> 00:39:57,780
Aku sudah ingin pulang tidur.

678
00:39:59,300 --> 00:40:01,870
Semester baru mulai, jangan ngeluh terus.

679
00:40:02,110 --> 00:40:03,580
Ngantuk banget aku.

680
00:40:04,870 --> 00:40:07,350
Apaan sih kalian.

681
00:40:07,480 --> 00:40:10,000
Kenapa, Foam? Mau bolos, ya?

682
00:40:10,240 --> 00:40:11,320
Boleh, nggak?

683
00:40:16,030 --> 00:40:17,980
Bisa nitip absen ke kamu besok?

684
00:40:20,560 --> 00:40:22,130
Jangan harap.

685
00:40:22,420 --> 00:40:25,720
Foam, kamu nggak bisa kayak SMA lagi.

686
00:40:25,720 --> 00:40:28,450
Kalau di kuliah gagal, akibatnya berat, lho.

687
00:40:28,480 --> 00:40:29,880
Kalian berdua cerewet banget.

688
00:40:29,880 --> 00:40:31,800
Lebih cerewet dari orangtuaku.

689
00:40:32,190 --> 00:40:34,180
Gara-gara kamu nggak fokus di kelas.

690
00:40:34,180 --> 00:40:35,790
Emang kamu serius di kelas?

691
00:40:35,870 --> 00:40:37,650
Itu juga karena kamu suka ngajak ngobrol.

692
00:40:38,970 --> 00:40:41,830
Udah ah, ribut, nanti guru marah.

693
00:40:41,860 --> 00:40:42,990
Fokus, dong.

694
00:40:43,010 --> 00:40:44,400
Aku pengen bolos.

695
00:40:50,140 --> 00:40:53,650
Teman-teman, cukup sampai sini.
Kita bubar.

696
00:40:53,940 --> 00:40:55,640
Terima kasih, Pak.

697
00:40:56,120 --> 00:40:57,640
-Sudah selesai? -Iya.

698
00:41:01,010 --> 00:41:01,840
Sesuai permintaanmu.

699
00:41:02,730 --> 00:41:04,750
Kalian mau pulang sekarang?

700
00:41:04,830 --> 00:41:07,020
Kita ada acara klub hari ini. Lupa?

701
00:41:07,950 --> 00:41:09,530
Oh, iya!

702
00:41:10,490 --> 00:41:12,370
-Kalian ikut juga? -Iya.

703
00:41:12,420 --> 00:41:14,530
Aku sama North sudah janji ke Daotok.

704
00:41:14,550 --> 00:41:17,030
Aku mau mampir dulu sebelum pulang.

705
00:41:17,410 --> 00:41:18,740
Kalau kamu, Phoon?

706
00:41:18,890 --> 00:41:21,390
Kalau Ter ikut, aku juga ikut.

707
00:41:21,720 --> 00:41:23,050
Kalau gitu aku juga.

708
00:41:23,160 --> 00:41:24,260
Ayo berangkat.

709
00:41:25,470 --> 00:41:27,620
Nggak ada hubungannya sama pelajaran.

710
00:41:27,700 --> 00:41:29,620
Kok kamu gampang banget setuju?

711
00:41:36,350 --> 00:41:37,270
Bro.

712
00:41:37,710 --> 00:41:39,380
Kenapa nggak ada yang daftar klub kita?

713
00:41:42,840 --> 00:41:44,460
Kapan Ter datang?

714
00:41:44,580 --> 00:41:45,750
Katanya dia sudah sampai.

715
00:41:45,840 --> 00:41:49,240
Tapi dia bawa Foam ke klub lain.

716
00:41:49,470 --> 00:41:51,660
North, kamu juga mau daftar klub lain?

717
00:41:53,240 --> 00:41:54,970
Aku belum tahu.

718
00:41:55,100 --> 00:41:56,260
Mungkin daftar beberapa juga.

719
00:41:56,310 --> 00:41:58,260
Nanti saja aku lihat-lihat lagi.

720
00:41:58,460 --> 00:42:01,190
Kamu kenal yang mau gabung klub nggak?

721
00:42:01,360 --> 00:42:02,930
Bisa saja kamu ajak gabung klub kita.

722
00:42:02,930 --> 00:42:05,140
Kenapa? Sedikit orang malah lebih baik.

723
00:42:05,220 --> 00:42:06,620
