726
00:42:12,760 --> 00:42:16,400
Aku coba tanya teman di jurusan teknik, siapa tahu mau gabung.

727
00:42:16,680 --> 00:42:18,790
Lihat, ada nih.

728
00:42:21,030 --> 00:42:21,890
Hei.

729
00:42:22,270 --> 00:42:24,270
Bisa minta Ter hubungi senior fakultas kedokteran.

730
00:42:24,680 --> 00:42:26,460
Temannya banyak, loh.

731
00:42:26,860 --> 00:42:27,960
Senior angkatan atas di kedokteran?

732
