770
00:44:33,200 --> 00:44:35,450
Kamu mau ikut klub sepak bola?

771
00:44:35,910 --> 00:44:38,530
-Iya. -Aku juga, mau ikut.

772
00:44:38,840 --> 00:44:42,090
Gimana, Fah? Mau daftar? Jo?

773
00:44:45,720 --> 00:44:48,750
Ter, sudah gabung klub mana?

774
00:44:48,770 --> 00:44:51,490
Sebenarnya aku sudah gabung klub melukis.

775
00:44:51,880 --> 00:44:53,960
-Klub melukis? -Iya.

776
00:44:55,610 --> 00:44:57,400
Mau mampir ke klubku?

777
00:44:57,800 --> 00:44:59,290
Lagi butuh anggota, lho.

778
00:44:59,610 --> 00:45:00,780
Ayo, yuk.

779
00:45:02,000 --> 00:45:03,800
Ayo, kita ke sana.

780
00:45:07,330 --> 00:45:10,670
Fah, gabung klub sepak bolaku dong.

781
00:45:11,310 --> 00:45:12,720
-Aduh... -Ayo dong!

782
00:45:12,760 --> 00:45:15,190
-Aku nggak enak, deh. -Ayo dong!

783
00:45:15,220 --> 00:45:17,630
Klubku latihan tiap Jumat di gedung seni lama.

784
00:45:17,900 --> 00:45:20,100
Datang pukul empat, paling lambat enam sudah selesai.

785
00:45:22,830 --> 00:45:24,120
