786
00:45:24,170 --> 00:45:25,080
Kalau P'Hill ikut gabung,

787
00:45:25,080 --> 00:45:27,960
pasti makin banyak yang mau gabung klub.

788
00:45:29,210 --> 00:45:30,660
Serius.

789
00:45:36,290 --> 00:45:38,610
Apa yang kamu bilang soal Daotok tadi?

790
00:45:39,170 --> 00:45:41,650
Serius? Aku bilang apa memangnya?

791
00:45:42,250 --> 00:45:43,650
Kamu bohong padaku.

792
00:45:44,330 --> 00:45:45,490
Tolong aku!

793
00:45:46,280 --> 00:45:48,250
Boleh aku daftarkan temanku juga?

794
00:45:48,290 --> 00:45:49,800
Ya.

795
00:45:50,000 --> 00:45:50,840
Hebat sekali, P'Hill!

796
00:45:50,840 --> 00:45:52,930
Tolong tulis lebih banyak, makin banyak makin baik.

797
00:45:56,190 --> 00:45:59,850
Ada rencana setelah ini? Mau ke mana nanti?

798
00:46:00,250 --> 00:46:01,480
Tidak ada rencana.

799
00:46:01,700 --> 00:46:03,050
Mau makan sesuatu?

800
00:46:03,100 --> 00:46:03,850
Hmm.

801
00:46:04,190 --> 00:46:06,000
Kamu mau makan apa?

802
00:46:06,220 --> 00:46:08,230
Apa saja, terserah kamu.

803
00:46:08,710 --> 00:46:10,000
Mau ke pasar?

804
00:46:10,780 --> 00:46:12,510
Ayo.

805
00:46:13,620 --> 00:46:14,960
-Sampai jumpa. -Sampai jumpa, P'Hill.

806
00:46:14,970 --> 00:46:16,950
-Kita berangkat sekarang? -Ayo.

807
00:46:22,500 --> 00:46:25,810
Itu yang kamu sebut Kemeja Mo Hom?

808
00:46:25,820 --> 00:46:26,830
Ya.

809
00:46:26,840 --> 00:46:28,250
Kamu mau satu?

810
00:46:28,280 --> 00:46:29,650
Tidak perlu.

811
00:46:29,690 --> 00:46:31,070
Kelihatan bagus, kok.

812
00:46:31,240 --> 00:46:32,630
Celana gajah itu juga lucu banget.

813
00:46:32,730 --> 00:46:34,380
Kelihatannya sangat nyaman dipakai.

814
00:46:34,400 --> 00:46:35,620
Mau punya satu?

815
00:46:36,480 --> 00:46:37,610
