Kamu bisa tersesat nanti.

818
00:46:56,370 --> 00:46:57,460
Kenapa?

819
00:46:57,980 --> 00:46:59,530
Kamu nggak mau orang lain lihat?

820
00:47:00,420 --> 00:47:01,560
Bukan begitu.

821
00:47:01,750 --> 00:47:04,240
Rasanya agak aneh saja.

822
00:47:05,230 --> 00:47:06,780
Kenapa begitu?

823
00:47:06,990 --> 00:47:08,580
Mungkin aku belum terbiasa.

824
00:47:09,180 --> 00:47:12,100
Kalau begitu harus sering pegang,
biar nanti kamu terbiasa.

825
00:47:16,490 --> 00:47:17,690
Halo.

826
00:47:17,690 --> 00:47:19,540
Hai, ini minuman longan favoritku.

827
00:47:19,750 --> 00:47:20,790
Aku pesan satu.

828
00:47:20,930 --> 00:47:22,070
Jangan terlalu manis, ya.

829
00:47:33,250 --> 00:47:34,420
Gimana rasanya?

830
00:47:35,260 --> 00:47:36,520
Mau coba?

831
00:47:38,780 --> 00:47:40,510
Enak nggak?

832
00:47:44,210 --> 00:47:45,790
Maaf ya.

833
00:48:00,380 --> 00:48:01,370
Ini.

834
00:48:02,890 --> 00:48:03,970
Terima kasih.

835
00:48:03,990 --> 00:48:05,120
Boleh aku yang bayar?

836
00:48:05,120 --> 00:48:07,270
Aku nggak mau kamu terus-terusan bayar.

837
00:48:07,910 --> 00:48:11,350
Kalau begitu, tukar dengan sesuatu yang lain, ya.

838
00:48:11,410 --> 00:48:12,690
Apa itu?

839
00:48:12,750 --> 00:48:14,300
Belum mau kasih tahu.

840
00:48:15,140 --> 00:48:16,730
Mau yang lain?

841
00:48:17,970 --> 00:48:19,890
Belum tahu, aku mau lihat-lihat dulu.

842
00:48:19,980 --> 00:48:22,620
Oke, ayo lanjut.

843
00:48:24,740 --> 00:48:26,500
Bagus nggak ini?

844
00:48:42,240 --> 00:48:43,800
Kamu nggak makan?

845
00:48:45,830 --> 00:48:46,950
Makan, kok.

846
00:48:48,510 --> 00:48:49,670
Suapin aku.

847
00:48:52,520 --> 00:48:53,810
Jangan, ah.

848
00:48:54,270 --> 00:48:55,700
Ayolah~.

849
00:49:00,390 --> 00:49:01,530
Ayo.

850
00:49:08,630 --> 00:49:10,740
Gimana? Enak nggak?

851
